rows.label: tlk45710153_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Hmm? Have we met somewhere
before, perhaps?

rows.label: tlk45710153_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Ah, the Chairman's office in Goldmund.
Of course, of course...

rows.label: tlk45710153_01_msg0003
rows.name:
This is where I grew up, you know.
I came back briefly to take care of
a small work-related matter...

rows.label: tlk45710153_01_msg0004
rows.name:
And now that's all sorted, I'm enjoying
a sweet moment's rest.

rows.label: tlk45710153_01_msg0005
rows.name:
I wouldn't recommend you stray too
close to Hadashal Palace, by the way.
It's just across that bridge there.

rows.label: tlk45710153_01_msg0006
rows.name:
If you're lucky, you'd get turned away
by the guards. If you're unlucky, you
might wind up in a cell.
